1: Create Folder - ExpressPorfolioSite
2: Create Folder - Scripts // not needed in the future
3: Create index.js // not needed in the future
    -run: npm init
    -set up server
    -run: node index.js
    -install nodemon: npm install -g nodemon
        -run nodemon: nodemon
    -install express: npm install express -save
        -set up server in the index.js and run
    -make simple routes(using get)
    -install express-generator: npm install -g express-generator
        -run: express -e
    -install remaining packages in package.json: npm install
4: run: npm start (for express)
        move www to outside and name it to server.js
        change start point in package.json to server.js
        delete bin Folder
5: install - .ejs 0.1
6: organize public folder by creating and deleting files and folders
7. Add routes in routes/index.js
8. start work on views/index.ejs
9. install bootstrap: npm install bootstrap --save
10. install jquery: npm install jquery --save
11. install proper.js: npm install popper.js --save
12. install font-awesome: npm install @fortawesome/fontawesome-free --save
13. app.js : app.use(express.static(path.join(__dirname, 'node_modules')));
14. set path for bootstrap/jquery....
